{"word":"βόσκω","slug":"βόσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>βόσϰω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> complex, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ perh.\">perh.</a> a connection <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βοῦς\">βοῦς</a></el>; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prim.\">prim.</a> of a herdsman’s task ‘to feed’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘tend to needs of animals’, <b><i>herd, tend</i> <a href='B:470 8:33'>Mt 8:33</a>; <a href='B:480 5:14'>Mk 5:14</a>; <a href='B:490 8:34'>Lk 8:34</a>; <a href='B:490 15:15'>15:15</a>.</b> In imagery<b> <a href='B:500 21:15'>J 21:15</a>, <a href='B:500 21:17'>17</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> sense of 1: <b><i>graze, feed</i> <a href='B:470 8:30'>Mt 8:30</a>; <a href='B:480 5:11'>Mk 5:11</a>; <a href='B:490 8:32'>Lk 8:32</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βορρᾶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Βοσόρ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}